{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1031,"text":"My students often ask me,\n\"What is sociology?\""},{"time":5558,"text":"And I tell them it's the study of the way\nin which human beings are shaped"},{"time":9934,"text":"by things that they don't see."},{"time":12501,"text":"And they say, \"So,\nhow can I be a sociologist?"},{"time":16660,"text":"How can I understand\nthose invisible forces?\""},{"time":18802,"text":"And I say, \"Empathy."},{"time":20354,"text":"Start with empathy."},{"time":22478,"text":"It all begins with empathy."},{"time":25284,"text":"Take yourself out of your shoes,"},{"time":27064,"text":"put yourself into the shoes\nof another person.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":29732,"text":"Here, I'll give you an example."},{"time":32263,"text":"So I imagine my life\nif, a hundred years ago,"},{"time":35691,"text":"China had been the most powerful\nnation in the world"},{"time":38565,"text":"and they came to the United States\nin search of coal."},{"time":42076,"text":"And they found it, and, in fact,\nthey found lots of it right here."},{"time":45291,"text":"And pretty soon,\nthey began shipping that coal,"},{"time":48841,"text":"ton by ton,"},{"time":50641,"text":"railcar by railcar, boatload by boatload,"},{"time":54103,"text":"back to China and elsewhere\naround the world."},{"time":58069,"text":"And they got fabulously\nwealthy in doing so."},{"time":60343,"text":"And they built beautiful cities"},{"time":62700,"text":"all powered on that coal."},{"time":67612,"text":"And back here in the United States,"},{"time":71057,"text":"we saw economic despair, deprivation."},{"time":73228,"text":"This is what I saw."},{"time":74700,"text":"I saw people struggling to get by,"},{"time":77355,"text":"not knowing what was what\nand what was next."},{"time":80474,"text":"And I asked myself the question:"},{"time":82765,"text":"How is it possible that we could\nbe so poor here in the United States,"},{"time":86119,"text":"because coal is such a wealthy\nresource; it's so much money?"},{"time":89848,"text":"And I realize:"},{"time":91032,"text":"because the Chinese ingratiated themselves"},{"time":94461,"text":"with a small ruling class\nhere in the United States,"},{"time":97244,"text":"who stole all of that money\nand all of that wealth for themselves."},{"time":101430,"text":"And the rest of us,\nthe vast majority of us,"},{"time":103620,"text":"struggle to get by."},{"time":105389,"text":"And the Chinese\ngave this small ruling elite"},{"time":108517,"text":"loads of military weapons\nand sophisticated technology"},{"time":111910,"text":"in order to ensure that people like me"},{"time":114700,"text":"would not speak out\nagainst this relationship."},{"time":118573,"text":"Does this sound familiar?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":121445,"text":"And they did things like train Americans\nto help protect the coal."},{"time":125056,"text":"And everywhere, there were\nsymbols of the Chinese --"},{"time":128318,"text":"everywhere, a constant reminder."},{"time":131931,"text":"And back in China,"},{"time":134098,"text":"what do they say in China?"},{"time":135448,"text":"Nothing! They don't talk about us.\nThey don't talk about the coal."},{"time":139071,"text":"If you ask them,"},{"time":140285,"text":"they'll say, \"Well, you know,\nwe need the coal."},{"time":142700,"text":"I mean, come on, I'm not going\nto turn down my thermostat."},{"time":146422,"text":"You can't expect that.\""},{"time":148374,"text":"And so, I get angry, and I get pissed,"},{"time":151573,"text":"as do lots of average people."},{"time":153910,"text":"And we fight back,\nand it gets really ugly."},{"time":156476,"text":"And the Chinese respond\nin a very ugly way."},{"time":160620,"text":"And before we know it,\nthey send in the tanks"},{"time":163039,"text":"and they send in the troops."},{"time":165382,"text":"And lots of people are dying."},{"time":167700,"text":"And it's a very, very difficult situation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":172676,"text":"Can you imagine what you would feel"},{"time":175747,"text":"if you were in my shoes?"},{"time":177936,"text":"Can you imagine\nwalking out of this building"},{"time":180285,"text":"and seeing a tank sitting out there,"},{"time":182127,"text":"or a truck full of soldiers?"},{"time":185900,"text":"Just imagine what you would feel,\nbecause you know why they're here;"},{"time":189144,"text":"you know what they're doing here."},{"time":190814,"text":"And you just feel the anger\nand you feel the fear."},{"time":194374,"text":"If you can, that's empathy.\nThat's empathy."},{"time":197164,"text":"You've left your shoes,\nand you've stood in mine."},{"time":201138,"text":"And you've got to feel that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":202977,"text":"OK, so that's the warm-up."},{"time":205056,"text":"That's the warm-up."},{"time":206252,"text":"Now we're going to have\nthe real radical experiment."},{"time":210010,"text":"So, for the remainder of my talk,\nwhat I want you to do"},{"time":213700,"text":"is put yourselves in the shoes\nof an ordinary Arab Muslim"},{"time":218312,"text":"living in the Middle East --"},{"time":220065,"text":"in particular, in Iraq."},{"time":224343,"text":"And so to help you,"},{"time":226271,"text":"perhaps you're a member\nof this middle-class family in Baghdad."},{"time":230604,"text":"What you want is the best for your kids."},{"time":233322,"text":"You want your kids to have a better life."},{"time":235323,"text":"And you watch the news, you pay attention."},{"time":237434,"text":"You read the newspaper, you go down\nto the coffee shop with your friends,"},{"time":241012,"text":"you read the newspapers\nfrom around the world."},{"time":243257,"text":"Sometimes you even watch satellite,\nCNN, from the United States."},{"time":246317,"text":"You have a sense of what\nthe Americans are thinking."},{"time":248828,"text":"But really, you just want\na better life for yourself."},{"time":251900,"text":"That's what you want."},{"time":253445,"text":"You're Arab Muslim living in Iraq."},{"time":256533,"text":"You want a better life for yourself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":258304,"text":"So here, let me help you."},{"time":259542,"text":"Let me help you with some things\nthat you might be thinking."},{"time":263057,"text":"Number one:"},{"time":264350,"text":"this incursion into your land\nthese past 20 years and before --"},{"time":268700,"text":"the reason anyone\nis interested in your land,"},{"time":270843,"text":"and particularly\nthe United States, is oil."},{"time":273011,"text":"It's all about oil; you know that,\neverybody knows that."},{"time":276144,"text":"People back in the United States\nknow it's about oil."},{"time":279459,"text":"It's because somebody else\nhas a design for your resource."},{"time":284581,"text":"It's your resource --\nit's not somebody else's."},{"time":287158,"text":"It's your land; it's your resource."},{"time":290160,"text":"Somebody else has a design for it."},{"time":292778,"text":"And you know why they have a design?"},{"time":294655,"text":"You know why they have\ntheir eyes set on it?"},{"time":296776,"text":"Because they have\nan entire economic system"},{"time":298874,"text":"that's dependent\non that oil -- foreign oil,"},{"time":302107,"text":"oil from other parts of the world\nthat they don't own."}]},{"cues":[{"time":305247,"text":"And what else do you think\nabout these people?"},{"time":307838,"text":"The Americans, they're rich."},{"time":309270,"text":"Come on, they live in big houses,\nthey have big cars."},{"time":311815,"text":"They all have blond hair,\nblue eyes. They're happy."},{"time":314239,"text":"You think that. It's not true, of course,\nbut that's the media impression."},{"time":317772,"text":"And that's what you get."},{"time":318992,"text":"And they have big cities,"},{"time":320224,"text":"and the cities are all dependent on oil."},{"time":324700,"text":"And back home, what do you see?"},{"time":326700,"text":"Poverty, despair, struggle."},{"time":329216,"text":"Look, you don't live in a wealthy country."},{"time":331632,"text":"I mean -- this is Iraq."},{"time":335275,"text":"This is what you see."},{"time":337212,"text":"You see people struggling to get by."},{"time":339873,"text":"It's not easy; you see a lot of poverty."},{"time":341966,"text":"And you feel something about this."},{"time":343657,"text":"These people have designs\nfor your resource,"},{"time":345778,"text":"and this is what you see?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":347982,"text":"Something else you see\nthat you talk about --"},{"time":350118,"text":"Americans don't talk\nabout this, but you do --"},{"time":352352,"text":"there's this thing,\nthis militarization of the world,"},{"time":354903,"text":"and it's centered\nright in the United States."},{"time":357071,"text":"And the United States is responsible"},{"time":358969,"text":"for almost one half\nof the world's military spending."},{"time":364264,"text":"Four percent of the world's population!"},{"time":366280,"text":"And you feel it; you see it every day."},{"time":368848,"text":"It's part of your life."},{"time":370194,"text":"And you talk about it with your friends."},{"time":372996,"text":"You read about it."},{"time":374608,"text":"And back when Saddam Hussein was in power,"},{"time":378486,"text":"the Americans didn't care\nabout his crimes."},{"time":381411,"text":"When he was gassing\nthe Kurds and gassing Iran,"},{"time":383852,"text":"they didn't care about it."},{"time":385351,"text":"When oil was at stake,"},{"time":387454,"text":"somehow, suddenly, things mattered."},{"time":392485,"text":"And what you see, something else:"},{"time":394911,"text":"the United States,"},{"time":396721,"text":"the hub of democracy around the world --"},{"time":398854,"text":"they don't seem to really be supporting\ndemocratic countries"},{"time":402517,"text":"all around the world."},{"time":404428,"text":"There are a lot of countries,\noil-producing countries,"},{"time":407171,"text":"that aren't very democratic,\nbut supported by the United States."},{"time":411130,"text":"That's odd."}]},{"cues":[{"time":412317,"text":"Oh -- these incursions, these two wars,"},{"time":415142,"text":"the 10 years of sanctions,"},{"time":417478,"text":"the eight years of occupation,"},{"time":421173,"text":"the insurgency that's been\nunleashed on your people,"},{"time":424851,"text":"the tens of thousands,\nthe hundreds of thousands"},{"time":427700,"text":"of civilian deaths?"},{"time":432914,"text":"All because of oil."},{"time":435628,"text":"You can't help but think that."},{"time":437588,"text":"You talk about it."},{"time":439700,"text":"It's in the forefront\nof your mind, always."},{"time":442700,"text":"You say, \"How is that possible?\""},{"time":445207,"text":"And this man, he's everyman --"},{"time":448700,"text":"your grandfather, your uncle,"},{"time":450775,"text":"your father, your son, your neighbor,"},{"time":452862,"text":"your professor, your student."},{"time":455092,"text":"Once a life of happiness and joy"},{"time":457995,"text":"and suddenly, pain and sorrow."},{"time":462100,"text":"Everyone in your country\nhas been touched by the violence,"},{"time":468338,"text":"the bloodshed, the pain,\nthe horror -- everybody."},{"time":471447,"text":"Not a single person in your country\nhas not been touched."}]},{"cues":[{"time":477124,"text":"But there's something else."},{"time":478700,"text":"There's something else about these people,\nthese Americans who are there."},{"time":482700,"text":"There's something else\nabout them that you see"},{"time":484925,"text":"that they don't see themselves."},{"time":486523,"text":"And what do you see? They're Christians!"},{"time":488699,"text":"They're Christians."},{"time":490191,"text":"They worship the Christian God,\nthey have crosses, they carry Bibles."},{"time":493716,"text":"Their Bibles have a little insignia"},{"time":495898,"text":"that says \"US Army\" on them."},{"time":499700,"text":"And their leaders, their leaders:"},{"time":502700,"text":"before they send their sons and daughters\noff to war in your country --"},{"time":507017,"text":"and you know the reason --"},{"time":508379,"text":"before they send them off,"},{"time":509970,"text":"they go to a Christian church,\nand they pray to their Christian God,"},{"time":513296,"text":"and they ask for protection\nand guidance from that god."},{"time":516104,"text":"Why?"},{"time":517305,"text":"Well, obviously,\nwhen people die in the war,"},{"time":521382,"text":"they are Muslims, they are Iraqis --\nthey're not Americans."},{"time":525985,"text":"You don't want Americans to die --\n\"Protect Our Troops.\""},{"time":528829,"text":"And you feel something about that --"},{"time":531184,"text":"of course you do."},{"time":532411,"text":"And they do wonderful things."},{"time":534362,"text":"You read about it, you hear about it."},{"time":536200,"text":"They're there to build schools\nand help people."},{"time":538442,"text":"That's what they want to do."},{"time":539835,"text":"They do wonderful things,\nbut they also do the bad things,"},{"time":542627,"text":"and you can't tell the difference."}]},{"cues":[{"time":544286,"text":"And this guy, you get a guy\nlike Lt. Gen. William Boykin."},{"time":547077,"text":"Here's a guy who says\nthat your god is a false god."},{"time":549598,"text":"Your god's an idol;\nhis god is the true god."},{"time":551700,"text":"The solution to the problem\nin the Middle East, according to him,"},{"time":554820,"text":"is to convert you all to Christianity --"},{"time":556778,"text":"just get rid of your religion."},{"time":558700,"text":"And you know that.\nAmericans don't read about this guy."},{"time":561435,"text":"They don't know anything\nabout him, but you do."},{"time":563700,"text":"You pass it around.\nYou pass his words around."},{"time":565915,"text":"I mean, this is serious. You're afraid."},{"time":568511,"text":"He was one of the leading commanders\nin the second invasion of Iraq."},{"time":571775,"text":"And you're thinking,\n\"My God, if this guy is saying that,"},{"time":574513,"text":"then all the soldiers\nmust be saying that.\""},{"time":577112,"text":"And this word here --"},{"time":578621,"text":"George Bush called this war a crusade."},{"time":580558,"text":"Man, the Americans,\nthey're just like, \"Ah, crusade."},{"time":583060,"text":"Whatever. I don't know what that means.\""},{"time":585030,"text":"You know what it means --\nit's a holy war against Muslims."},{"time":588079,"text":"Look, invade, subdue them,\ntake their resources."},{"time":591932,"text":"If they won't submit, kill them."},{"time":594205,"text":"That's what this is about."},{"time":595580,"text":"And you're thinking, \"My God,\nthese Christians are coming to kill us.\""},{"time":599232,"text":"This is frightening."},{"time":600700,"text":"You feel frightened.\nOf course you feel frightened."}]},{"cues":[{"time":603478,"text":"And this man, Terry Jones:"},{"time":606199,"text":"I mean here's a guy\nwho wants to burn Qurans, right?"},{"time":608970,"text":"And the Americans:\n\"Ah, he's a knucklehead."},{"time":611647,"text":"He's a former hotel manager; he's got\nthree dozen members of his church ...\""},{"time":615300,"text":"They laugh him off."},{"time":616491,"text":"You don't laugh him off,\nbecause in the context of everything else,"},{"time":619701,"text":"all the pieces fit."},{"time":620876,"text":"Of course this is how Americans think."},{"time":622784,"text":"So people all over the Middle East,\nnot just in your country,"},{"time":625811,"text":"are protesting."},{"time":626991,"text":"\"He wants to burn Qurans, our holy book."},{"time":628946,"text":"These Christians --\nwho are these Christians?"},{"time":631098,"text":"They're so evil, they're so mean --\nthis is what they're about?\""},{"time":634537,"text":"This is what you're thinking\nas an Arab Muslim,"},{"time":637176,"text":"as an Iraqi."},{"time":638609,"text":"Of course you're going to think this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":640610,"text":"And then your cousin says,\n\"Hey coz, check out this website."},{"time":644558,"text":"You've got to see this -- Bible Boot Camp."},{"time":646856,"text":"These Christians are nuts!"},{"time":648158,"text":"They're training their little kids\nto be soldiers for Jesus."},{"time":651049,"text":"They take little kids\nand run them through these things"},{"time":653658,"text":"till they teach them\nhow to say, 'Sir! Yes, sir!'"},{"time":655984,"text":"and things like 'grenade toss'\nand 'weapons care and maintenance.'"},{"time":659120,"text":"And go to the website --\nit says 'US Army' right on it."},{"time":662176,"text":"I mean, these Christians, they're nuts."},{"time":664110,"text":"How can they do this\nto their little kids?\""},{"time":666144,"text":"And you're reading this website."},{"time":667699,"text":"And of course, Christians\nin the United States, or anybody,"},{"time":670544,"text":"says, \"This is some little church\nin the middle of nowhere.\""},{"time":673449,"text":"You don't know that."},{"time":674624,"text":"For you, this is like, all Christians."},{"time":677057,"text":"It's all over the Web: \"Bible Boot Camp.\""},{"time":679383,"text":"And look at this."},{"time":681157,"text":"They even teach their kids --"},{"time":682576,"text":"they train them in the same way\nthe US Marines train."},{"time":685907,"text":"Isn't that interesting."},{"time":687398,"text":"And it scares you, and it frightens you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":689700,"text":"So these guys, you see them."},{"time":691700,"text":"You see, I, Sam Richards --\nI know who these guys are."},{"time":694908,"text":"They're my students, my friends;\nI know what they're thinking."},{"time":697865,"text":"You don't know."},{"time":699097,"text":"When you see them, they're something else."},{"time":702426,"text":"They're something else."},{"time":704130,"text":"That's what they are to you."},{"time":706908,"text":"We don't see it that way\nin the United States,"},{"time":709399,"text":"but you see it that way."},{"time":714700,"text":"So here."},{"time":716501,"text":"Of course, you've got it wrong."},{"time":718557,"text":"You're generalizing. It's wrong."},{"time":721064,"text":"You don't understand the Americans."},{"time":723375,"text":"It's not a Christian invasion."},{"time":725079,"text":"We're not just there for oil;\nwe're there for lots of reasons."},{"time":728076,"text":"You have it wrong. You've missed it."},{"time":730113,"text":"And of course, most of you\ndon't support the insurgency;"},{"time":732914,"text":"you don't support killing Americans;"},{"time":734696,"text":"you don't support the terrorists."},{"time":736700,"text":"Of course you don't. Very few people do."},{"time":738700,"text":"But -- some of you do."},{"time":741972,"text":"And this is a perspective."},{"time":743781,"text":"OK. So now, here's what we're going to do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":746537,"text":"Step outside of your shoes\nthat you're in right now,"},{"time":750522,"text":"and step back into your normal shoes."},{"time":752336,"text":"So everyone's back in the room. OK?"},{"time":755265,"text":"Now here comes the radical experiment."},{"time":757190,"text":"So we're all back home."},{"time":759216,"text":"This photo: this woman --"},{"time":761332,"text":"man, I feel her."},{"time":763229,"text":"I feel her."},{"time":764826,"text":"She's my sister,"},{"time":766330,"text":"my wife, my cousin, my neighbor."},{"time":769538,"text":"She's anybody to me."},{"time":770958,"text":"These guys standing there,\neverybody in the photo --"},{"time":773689,"text":"I feel this photo, man."},{"time":776832,"text":"So here's what I want you to do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":778491,"text":"Let's go back to my first\nexample, of the Chinese."},{"time":782500,"text":"I want you to go there."},{"time":784346,"text":"It's all about coal, and the Chinese\nare here in the United States."},{"time":787600,"text":"What I want you to do is picture her"},{"time":789370,"text":"as a Chinese woman\nreceiving a Chinese flag"},{"time":792322,"text":"because her loved one has died\nin America in the coal uprising."},{"time":797612,"text":"And the soldiers are Chinese,"},{"time":799265,"text":"and everybody else is Chinese."},{"time":801620,"text":"As an American, how do you feel\nabout this picture?"},{"time":806930,"text":"What do you think about that scene?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":811700,"text":"OK, try this. Bring it back."},{"time":814246,"text":"This is the scene here."},{"time":815700,"text":"It's an American, American soldiers,"},{"time":817590,"text":"American woman who lost\nher loved one in the Middle East,"},{"time":820669,"text":"in Iraq or Afghanistan."},{"time":822896,"text":"Now, put yourself in the shoes,"},{"time":824896,"text":"go back to the shoes\nof an Arab Muslim living in Iraq."},{"time":831005,"text":"What are you feeling and thinking\nabout this photo,"},{"time":835827,"text":"about this woman?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":846001,"text":"OK,"},{"time":847700,"text":"now follow me on this,"},{"time":849700,"text":"because I'm taking a big risk here."},{"time":851855,"text":"And so I'm going to invite you\nto take a risk with me."},{"time":854618,"text":"These gentlemen here, they're insurgents."},{"time":856619,"text":"They were caught by the American soldiers,\ntrying to kill Americans."},{"time":860652,"text":"And maybe they succeeded.\nMaybe they succeeded."},{"time":864086,"text":"Put yourself in the shoes\nof the Americans who caught them."},{"time":869207,"text":"Can you feel the rage?"},{"time":871311,"text":"Can you feel that you just want\nto take these guys"},{"time":873717,"text":"and wring their necks?"},{"time":875191,"text":"Can you go there?"},{"time":877335,"text":"It shouldn't be that difficult."},{"time":879389,"text":"You just -- oh, man."},{"time":883274,"text":"Now, put yourself in their shoes."},{"time":890771,"text":"Are they brutal killers"},{"time":892772,"text":"or patriotic defenders?"},{"time":896701,"text":"Which one?"},{"time":898491,"text":"Can you feel their anger,"},{"time":901700,"text":"their fear,"},{"time":903155,"text":"their rage"},{"time":905824,"text":"at what has happened in their country?"},{"time":908045,"text":"Can you imagine that maybe\none of them, in the morning,"},{"time":912472,"text":"bent down to their child\nand hugged their child"},{"time":915628,"text":"and said, \"Dear, I'll be back later."},{"time":919629,"text":"I'm going out to defend\nyour freedom, your lives."},{"time":922982,"text":"I'm going out to look out for us,"},{"time":926469,"text":"the future of our country.\""},{"time":929080,"text":"Can you imagine that?"},{"time":930401,"text":"Can you imagine saying that?"},{"time":933128,"text":"Can you go there?"},{"time":937700,"text":"What do you think they're feeling?"},{"time":947723,"text":"You see, that's empathy."},{"time":949882,"text":"It's also understanding."}]},{"cues":[{"time":951350,"text":"[understand]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":953002,"text":"Now, you might ask,"},{"time":954334,"text":"\"OK, Sam, so why do you\ndo this sort of thing?"},{"time":957625,"text":"Why would you use\nthis example of all examples?\""},{"time":960009,"text":"And I say, because."},{"time":962700,"text":"You're allowed to hate these people."},{"time":964525,"text":"You're allowed to just hate them\nwith every fiber of your being."},{"time":969700,"text":"And if I can get you\nto step into their shoes"},{"time":973501,"text":"and walk an inch -- one tiny inch --"},{"time":977880,"text":"then imagine the kind\nof sociological analysis"},{"time":980618,"text":"that you can do in all other\naspects of your life."},{"time":985268,"text":"You can walk a mile"},{"time":986700,"text":"when it comes to understanding why\nthat person's driving 40 miles per hour"},{"time":991795,"text":"in the passing lane;"},{"time":993993,"text":"or your teenage son;"},{"time":996374,"text":"or your neighbor who annoys you\nby cutting his lawn on Sunday mornings."},{"time":1000041,"text":"Whatever it is, you can go so far."},{"time":1003501,"text":"And this is what I tell my students:"},{"time":1005620,"text":"step outside of your tiny, little world."},{"time":1009136,"text":"Step inside of the tiny,\nlittle world of somebody else."},{"time":1013889,"text":"And then do it again"},{"time":1015354,"text":"and do it again and do it again."},{"time":1017077,"text":"And suddenly, all these tiny,\nlittle worlds,"},{"time":1019210,"text":"they come together in this complex web."},{"time":1021486,"text":"And they build a big, complex world."},{"time":1024580,"text":"And suddenly, without realizing it,"},{"time":1026983,"text":"you're seeing the world differently."},{"time":1029184,"text":"Everything has changed."},{"time":1030971,"text":"Everything in your life has changed."},{"time":1033821,"text":"And that's, of course, what this is about."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1036918,"text":"Attend to other lives,"},{"time":1040064,"text":"other visions."},{"time":1041446,"text":"Listen to other people,"},{"time":1043895,"text":"enlighten ourselves."},{"time":1046509,"text":"I'm not saying that I support\nthe terrorists in Iraq."},{"time":1050779,"text":"But as a sociologist, what I am saying is:"},{"time":1054700,"text":"I understand."},{"time":1058700,"text":"And now perhaps -- perhaps -- you do, too."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1062952,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1064128,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}